{"tid":345501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鐵騎士倒地　貨車見義擋路","createTime":"2017-08-03T06:36:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T10:36:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c934a41c8bf4e9fe3bf116c394603ba80be8f22","tid":345501,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T06:36:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20110116&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170803\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20110116%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170803&d=oyvWpG%2BWImCkRdXppRAciwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=400296fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20110116%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170803&h=d148ba41\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20110116&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170803</a><br />\n<br />\n鐵騎士倒地　貨車見義擋路<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】一名南亞裔男子，昨晨駕駛電單車，沿黃大仙太子道東行駛，駛至采頤花園對開，電單車欲切往鄰線時，與一部載客小巴相撞，當場人仰車翻，鐵騎士倒地，手腳擦傷。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n南亞裔鐵騎士被撞後當場倒地，手腳擦傷。周鴻熙攝<br />\n<br />\n切線撞小巴出事<br />\n<br />\n尾隨一部貨車，司機見狀即停車，為傷者擋路，免他被其他車輛撞及，傷者稍後獲送院治理。昨晨8時許，26歲南亞漢駕駛電單車，沿太子道東2線東行，駛近采頤花園，電單車擬切往3線期間，遭一部由姓鄭（66歲）男子駕駛的紅頂小巴駛至撞倒，南亞鐵騎士當場墮地，躺在路上手腳擦傷淌血，當時一輛密斗貨車駛至，好心司機見狀即停下擋路，以防尾隨車輛輾過受傷鐵騎士，救護員稍後趕至，替傷者現場包紮敷治後，將其送院治理，警方正調查意外原因，現場交通輕微受阻。<br />\n■記者周鴻熙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170803/large/03la8p041.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170803%2Flarge%2F03la8p041.jpg&h=e7973808&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b3d2a29f25cd4798a1ff5c1a8a8d31be31157930","tid":345501,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T06:40:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"44e6ffc87d7ed5a2ab7d17922f81859ebfb8273e","tid":345501,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T06:54:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7d64df09ebb61ba7706d926898360aa3ac1e74a","tid":345501,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T10:31:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無啦啦停係到咪仲危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你意思係直接輾過去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5fcface668e48f71bb009b03e65e764c2501c57","tid":345501,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T10:36:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無啦啦停係到咪仲危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你意思係直接輾過去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n意思係學佢河南同鄉2個月前咁撚樣，有片自己search"}]}